com.example.zoomwroom.Entities

类 QRBucks

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.zoomwroom.Entities.QRBucks

  • public class QRBucks
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the QRBucks in the form of IOUs. They store the info about driveRequest via its ID as well as the amount owed. The status will be used in the future for the driver to collect the owed sum.
